


IMHSITORGB(3IM)        SDSC IMAGE LIBRARY         IMHSITORGB(3IM)



NAME
     ImHsiToRgb - Convert an HSI triplet to an RGB triplet

SYNOPSIS
     #include "im.h"

     void ImHsiToRgb( hsi, rgb )
          float     hsi[3];
          int  rgb[3];


DESCRIPTION
     ImHsiToRgb converts an HSI triplet in _h_s_i to an RGB  triplet
     returned in _r_g_b.

     Maximum and minimum values for the  different  color  values
     are:

           Channel     Minimum   Maximum    Type
8          ________________________________________
          red          0         255       Integer
          green        0         255       Integer
          blue         0         255       Integer
          hue          0.0       360.0     Integer
          saturation   0.0       1.0       Float
          intensity    0.0       1.0       Float

SEE ALSO
     ImIntro (3IM), ImErrNo (3IM), ImRgbToHsi (3IM)

